          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A sphere of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot-radius sphere from a point within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A target takes [[/r 8d6]] necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6786\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 2d6]] for each slot level above 6th.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
